'''Zappos'''是一家美国在线鞋类和服装零售商<ref name="Inc">{{Cite web|title=How I Did It: Tony Hsieh, CEO, Zappos.com|url=http://www.inc.com/magazine/20060901/hidi-hsieh.html|accessdate=October 11, 2007|author=Max Chafkin|year=2006|work=Inc.com|archive-date=2022-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220108110004/https://www.inc.com/magazine/20060901/hidi-hsieh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，总部位于美国[[内华达州|内华达州]][[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]。该公司由{{link-en|尼克·斯威姆|Nick Swinmurn}}于1999年创立，創立之初公司名為ShoeSite，網站域名為Shoesite.com。1999年7月，公司更名為Zappos<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Zappos Milestone: Timeline|url=https://footwearnews.com/2009/business/news/zappos-milestone-timeline-90566/|date=2009-05-04|last=Staff|first=F. N.|language=en|last2=Staff|first2=F. N.|website=Footwear News|access-date=2018-12-13|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204134957/https://footwearnews.com/2009/business/news/zappos-milestone-timeline-90566/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年7月，[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]收購Zappos<ref>{{Cite web|title=Here's Why Amazon Bought Zappos|url=https://mashable.com/2009/07/22/amazon-bought-zappos/|accessdate=2020-06-02|author=Parr|date=2009-07-22|first=Ben|work=Mashable|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204100147/https://mashable.com/2009/07/22/amazon-bought-zappos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

